{"tid":1318806,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新城市602大地震？","createTime":"2019-07-15T04:28:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-15T04:41:47.000Z","uid":68779,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5e3fb82e39e8eb7d4d37e3dc5ba93afd2b1c965f","tid":1318806,"uid":68779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T04:28:41.000Z","msg":"各位得閒可以去新城市management office 睇下 (帝都酒店新城市商業大廈602)<br />\n但聽講今日所有高級既都唔係到，點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n聽講話去哂灣仔HQ開會，仲要唔止新城市，其他大商場既都去哂果邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為依單野令其他商場都怕會受到新城市影響，全部人去哂傾點拆，其他場既人個個都係咁屌新城市果邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />依家暑假旺季其他場一早已經plan好哂點搞，條數仲要預計好靚仔。但依家，其他場個個都怕成為下一個新城市<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果大家有去開佢地既商場都知最近出左個儲分app<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/Qb0CjnJ/20190320-WTC-600x600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ibb.co%2FQb0CjnJ%2F20190320-WTC-600x600.jpg&h=e56885f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n依個app就要客人upload購物收據先儲到分，咁所以個商場每日做到幾多生意，邊間鋪頭生意額最多可以盡在掌握<br />\n但係聽人講尋日個場靜到爆炸，4樓儲分櫃位完全唔使排隊，就連大陸客換coupon個counter都仲有大把劵可以換，講緊以前中午就已經比大陸客換哂。星期日最旺既日子都比平日靜，甚至之前八號風球個場關左大半日都冇咁靜。依家有一日係咁已經大地震，真係想像唔到如果每個星期都有一次係咁會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ba30e082e2401c8c65e71101cd8f80607d292b7","tid":1318806,"uid":68779,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T04:29:29.000Z","msg":"沙田新城市廣場疑爆時代廣場翻版，新鴻基涉出租公共空間<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/news/art/20090807/13072650\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20090807%2F13072650&d=MD3su0BfWHBnm8Iidd6ZKVyVYJ%2BaYT2AGLfERhQaW2c%3D&h=3dfbd796\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20090807%2F13072650&h=428c386a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/news/art/20090807/13072650</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/ctJRq4C/Screen-Shot-2019-07-15-at-1-32-12-AM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ibb.co%2FctJRq4C%2FScreen-Shot-2019-07-15-at-1-32-12-AM.png&h=4af15227&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n地政署最近發現，沙田UA戲院所在的新城市廣場，近年翻新或涉違反地契條款，現正與發展商新鴻基地產研究改動工程有否超出樓面上限<br />\n<a href=\"https://newweb.hkgolden.com/thread/4048619/page/1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewweb.hkgolden.com%2Fthread%2F4048619%2Fpage%2F1&d=MD3su0BfWHBnm8Iidd6ZKVyVYJ%2BaYT2AGLfERhQaW2c%3D&h=2b498982\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://newweb.hkgolden.com/thread/4048619/page/1</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/QDxYWPj/Screen-Shot-2019-07-15-at-1-39-02-AM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ibb.co%2FQDxYWPj%2FScreen-Shot-2019-07-15-at-1-39-02-AM.png&h=8de88b39&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n發展商又想違規地契出租做展覽。根據新城市廣場地契，只能出租作非商業性質展覽。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/shatindistrict/photos/發展商又想違規地契出租做展覽根據新城市廣場地契只能出租作非商業性質展覽/1402469243096776/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fshatindistrict%2Fphotos%2F%E7%99%BC%E5%B1%95%E5%95%86%E5%8F%88%E6%83%B3%E9%81%95%E8%A6%8F%E5%9C%B0%E5%A5%91%E5%87%BA%E7%A7%9F%E5%81%9A%E5%B1%95%E8%A6%BD%E6%A0%B9%E6%93%9A%E6%96%B0%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%BB%A3%E5%A0%B4%E5%9C%B0%E5%A5%91%E5%8F%AA%E8%83%BD%E5%87%BA%E7%A7%9F%E4%BD%9C%E9%9D%9E%E5%95%86%E6%A5%AD%E6%80%A7%E8%B3%AA%E5%B1%95%E8%A6%BD%2F1402469243096776%2F&d=MD3su0BfWHBnm8Iidd6ZKVyVYJ%2BaYT2AGLfERhQaW2c%3D&h=054e7c48\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/shatindistrict/photos/發展商又想違規地契出租做展覽根據新城市廣場地契只能出租作非商業性質展覽/1402469243096776/</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/YTQz7c5/Screen-Shot-2019-07-15-at-1-31-10-AM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ibb.co%2FYTQz7c5%2FScreen-Shot-2019-07-15-at-1-31-10-AM.png&h=dd840c16&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n新城市廣場佔用公眾通道出租牟利<br />\n<a href=\"https://newweb.hkgolden.com/thread/1686030/page/1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewweb.hkgolden.com%2Fthread%2F1686030%2Fpage%2F1&d=MD3su0BfWHBnm8Iidd6ZKVyVYJ%2BaYT2AGLfERhQaW2c%3D&h=77252050\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://newweb.hkgolden.com/thread/1686030/page/1</a><br />\n以該處租金300元一呎，發展商在兩年內因此收租賺了超過2000多萬。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/ZN22Vjk/Screen-Shot-2019-07-15-at-1-57-54-AM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ibb.co%2FZN22Vjk%2FScreen-Shot-2019-07-15-at-1-57-54-AM.png&h=e60a71d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n地產商容許外賣店在商場「冒充」餐廳涉嫌無牌經營食肆<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.factwire.org/investigation/地產商容許外賣店在商場「冒充」餐廳涉嫌無牌經/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.factwire.org%2Finvestigation%2F%E5%9C%B0%E7%94%A2%E5%95%86%E5%AE%B9%E8%A8%B1%E5%A4%96%E8%B3%A3%E5%BA%97%E5%9C%A8%E5%95%86%E5%A0%B4%E3%80%8C%E5%86%92%E5%85%85%E3%80%8D%E9%A4%90%E5%BB%B3%E6%B6%89%E5%AB%8C%E7%84%A1%E7%89%8C%E7%B6%93%2F&d=MD3su0BfWHBnm8Iidd6ZKVyVYJ%2BaYT2AGLfERhQaW2c%3D&h=ec95cf87\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.factwire.org/investigation/地產商容許外賣店在商場「冒充」餐廳涉嫌無牌經/</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/MVsNTsW/Screen-Shot-2019-07-15-at-2-01-07-AM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ibb.co%2FMVsNTsW%2FScreen-Shot-2019-07-15-at-2-01-07-AM.png&h=fef35263&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n個位係L6, 以前係Pacific Coffee, 依家係咖啡店Elephant Grounds<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/Ld7SSpV/20170821174035-8-09.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ibb.co%2FLd7SSpV%2F20170821174035-8-09.jpg&h=75c6c49b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n留意一下左手邊企左個清潔姐姐，但點解唔會由餐廳員工自己清潔呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n原來依間鋪頭只係「外賣店」在商場「冒充」餐廳<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/0fqBWvz/Screen-Shot-2019-07-15-at-2-11-13-AM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ibb.co%2F0fqBWvz%2FScreen-Shot-2019-07-15-at-2-11-13-AM.png&h=0e6726e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有負責商場租賃的業內人士向傳真社透露，發展商在旗下商場的做法是鑽法律漏洞，容許、甚至教導僅持有外賣牌的商戶放置座位「冒充」餐廳，而事實上這些位置放置的座位，公眾人士不需任何消費也可以使用的。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/q0ykTJc/Screen-Shot-2019-07-15-at-2-11-26-AM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ibb.co%2Fq0ykTJc%2FScreen-Shot-2019-07-15-at-2-11-26-AM.png&h=e5927544&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/Npj48XF/Screen-Shot-2019-07-15-at-2-13-34-AM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ibb.co%2FNpj48XF%2FScreen-Shot-2019-07-15-at-2-13-34-AM.png&h=f0298b5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔知新城市廣場咁多年密密接job做一共搵左幾錢呢，再加埋將公共空間通道當店鋪面積出租既租金，應該都好和味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過更和味既係唔知政府有冇同新城市廣場追收番筆錢呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n例如好似時代廣場咁<br />\n港府指時代廣場濫用公地入稟索償<br />\nhttp://103.20.236.180/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=41638&amp;csid=261_341<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/0MQj7td/Screen-Shot-2019-07-15-at-1-44-05-AM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ibb.co%2F0MQj7td%2FScreen-Shot-2019-07-15-at-1-44-05-AM.png&h=0ce72b4e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n隔左咁多年，如果以現金租值計算，加埋咁多年既利息，筆數都幾和味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43222b0c1ade1466a0727ce7d1bc3424fbf2e585","tid":1318806,"uid":706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T04:29:34.000Z","msg":"最低成本既方法，又減低傷亡，和理非都可以幫手<br />\n請幫手推！！<br />\n<br />\n警告你地唔好再屌警察老母<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1317630\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1317630</a>"},{"pid":"28a7561c3e954615db36f6ff88d0fb2059680763","tid":1318806,"uid":4739,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T04:33:37.000Z","msg":"moko停車場見多人泊車仲加車<br />\n下次見人泊車排到出出面記得投訴"},{"pid":"1af6a176c702795dfebcdbae1ac8dbb759089c94","tid":1318806,"uid":68779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"28a7561c3e954615db36f6ff88d0fb2059680763","tid":1318806,"uid":4